{
  "script_id": "catmull-rom",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "给你一串散落的点，想画一条光滑曲线把它们连起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "而且这条曲线必须刚好穿过每一个点，一个都不能漏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "这正是 Catmull-Rom 样条要解决的问题：过点又平滑。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "tangent",
      "line_id": "tan-1",
      "filename": "tangent-tan-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/tangent-tan-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "要在两点之间平滑过渡，关键是知道曲线经过每个点时的方向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "tangent",
      "line_id": "tan-2",
      "filename": "tangent-tan-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/tangent-tan-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "Catmull-Rom 用一个巧妙的办法：某点的切线，等于它前后两点连线的方向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "tangent",
      "line_id": "tan-3",
      "filename": "tangent-tan-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/tangent-tan-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 43920,
      "text": "写成公式就是切线等于 P(i+1) 减 P(i-1) 再除以二。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-1",
      "filename": "formula-form-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/formula-form-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "有了两端的位置和切线，就能用三次多项式在中间插值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-2",
      "filename": "formula-form-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/formula-form-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "这四个条件对应一个固定的基矩阵，把四个相邻控制点加权混合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-3",
      "filename": "formula-form-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/formula-form-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "参数 t 从零走到一，曲线就从当前点平滑滑到下一个点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-1",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/compare-cmp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "同样一串控制点，B 样条只是被它们拉扯，并不真的穿过。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-2",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/compare-cmp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "这叫逼近；而 Catmull-Rom 老老实实过每个点，叫插值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-3",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/compare-cmp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "要精确经过路标就用插值，要更柔顺的整体形状就用逼近。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "试着拖动任意一个黑点，曲线会立刻跟过去并保持穿过它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "打开橙色的 B 样条对比，看两条曲线在同样点上有多不同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "Catmull-Rom 用相邻点估计切线，让曲线光滑地穿过每个控制点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "它是插值样条的代表，简单实用，动画路径里随处可见。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catmull-rom",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catmull-rom/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "记住插值过点、逼近不过点这条分界线，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 36.68,
  "total_size": 586800
}